            <ol>
                <li>
                    <p>
                        Toss a die <m>20</m> times.
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>
                        How many times does each number from <m>1</m> to <m>6</m> appear out of <m>20</m> tosses of a die? Record in the table below.
                    </p>
